Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Northern Antique Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Pandan, Province of Antique, to Governor Leandro Locsin Fullon General Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 754
An Act Changing the Name of the Northern Antique Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Pandan, Province of Antique, to Governor Leandro Locsin Fullon General Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Northern Antique Emergency Hospital in the Municipality of Pandan, Province of Antique, is changed to Governor Leandro Locsin Fullon General Hospital.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1a\^/phi1
Approved: April 13, 1984
